    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161280/extras/1ee42adb8a7341ca672eb161f746d27b.poster.avif?t=1728059993\" width=606 height=38 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161280/extras/1ee42adb8a7341ca672eb161f746d27b.webm?t=1728059993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161280/extras/1ee42adb8a7341ca672eb161f746d27b.mp4?t=1728059993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>自动式弹幕射击游戏加上随机 Roguelike 元素, 闪闪发光 RGB 三色原光属性是你的武器！充分利用光谱的力量，在面对不同敌人的弱点之间切换不同色调来打败敌人吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161280/extras/0b3fa655b7c8e6a9b4014038d9220af1.poster.avif?t=1728059993\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161280/extras/0b3fa655b7c8e6a9b4014038d9220af1.webm?t=1728059993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161280/extras/0b3fa655b7c8e6a9b4014038d9220af1.mp4?t=1728059993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在一个超越人来认知的平行宇宙里，光之少女掌控、创造并调节平行世界的可见光谱。邪恶的混沌势力俘虏了光之少女，企图汲取神圣的光之力量，将世界永远陷入黑暗。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161280/extras/a1d6eefd2a94e0f4c2c6cea1d2757b65.poster.avif?t=1728059993\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161280/extras/a1d6eefd2a94e0f4c2c6cea1d2757b65.webm?t=1728059993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161280/extras/a1d6eefd2a94e0f4c2c6cea1d2757b65.mp4?t=1728059993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>受到光之少女意志祝福的你犹如黑夜中的一丝光芒，你必须在接近无解的困境中崛起。多个强大的Boss挡在你拯救光之少女的路上，但只有你可以克服这一场灾难！<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 战略配上反应力-</h2> 特制的颜色匹配系统为传统弹幕射击游戏增加了更多趣味性<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >女神的祝福-</h2> 技能树自由组合系统带来更多独特的玩法<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >激情背景乐-</h2> 精心准备的战曲陪你拯救世界，曲目风格包括 DnB 鼓打贝斯和电子舞曲</li></ul>",
